title: Average ticket price of the New Orleans Saints 2006 to 2019
yAxis: Average ticket price in U.S. dollars
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Average ticket price in U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 13.
Overall Average ticket price in U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2009 and 2010.
The highest Average ticket price in U.S. dollars, of value 97.72 was reached at Year 2019
The lowest Average ticket price in U.S. dollars, of value 54.86 was reported at Year 2006, and 2007
